jakarta.nosql.mapping.keyvalue

Interface KeyValueWorkflow


  • public interface KeyValueWorkflow
    This implementation defines the workflow to insert an Entity on KeyValueTemplate. The default implementation follows:

    KeyValueEventPersistManager.firePreEntity(Object)

    KeyValueEventPersistManager.firePreKeyValueEntity(Object)

    KeyValueEntityConverter.toKeyValue(Object)

    KeyValueEventPersistManager.firePreKeyValue(KeyValueEntity)

    Database alteration

    KeyValueEventPersistManager.firePostKeyValue(KeyValueEntity)

    KeyValueEventPersistManager.firePostEntity(Object)

    KeyValueEventPersistManager.firePostKeyValueEntity(Object)
